description.excerpt: This repo lists recent contrastive learning papers, and includes code for many of them.
For the reference implementation of SoTA methods, (e.g., InstDis, CMC, MoCo, ...), see pycontrast.
PyTorch implementation of Contrastive Learning methods; List of awesome-contrastive-learning papers
